---

<section id="contacto">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Contacto</span>
    <div class="contact-wrapper">
      <h2 class="contact-title">Hablemos.</h2>
      <p class="contact-sub">
        Estoy buscando mi primera oportunidad como developer. Si tienes un proyecto interesante
        o una posición abierta, escríbeme.
      </p>

      <a href="mailto:cristiansg.dev@gmail.com" class="email-link mono">
        cristiansg.dev@gmail.com
      </a>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cristiansanchezgut/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="social-btn"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/>
            <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/>
            <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/>
          </svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/CristianSG2"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="social-btn"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"/>
            <path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/>
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #contacto {
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .contact-wrapper {
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  .contact-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .contact-sub {
    color: var(--subtext1);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.78;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .email-link {
    font-size: clamp(0.88rem, 2.2vw, 1.05rem);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 40%, transparent);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .email-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--subtext1);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .social-btn:hover {
    color: var(--text);
    border-color: var(--surface1);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
</style>
